PrecisOrder Amending the CANADIAN PASSPORT ORDER to the extent that parents will no longer be able to include children under 16 in their passport and that birth certificates issued by religious, judicial and municipal authorities will no longer be accepted as proof of citizenship, effective December 15, 2001.
